Implement functionality to ensure that all Decision-related email alerts are captured and stored in the Notification object for audit and tracking purposes.

Currently, decision email alerts are triggered but not consistently persisted. This enhancement will:

Capture all email alerts triggered from Decision status changes or events

Store them in the Notification object

Ensure the stored notification content matches the actual email sent

Provide traceability for all outbound email communications

This will improve visibility, compliance, and troubleshooting for decision-related communications.



Decision email alerts are stored in the Notification object

A Notification record is created for each email sent

Stored content matches the actual email (subject, body, recipients)

Notifications are triggered on Decision status changes/events

Related Decision record is linked to the Notification

System handles failures without breaking the process
